main.java.delivery

Class ColdTruck

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.delivery.Truck
      • main.java.delivery.ColdTruck

  • public class ColdTruck
extends Truck
    ColdTruck class used to store differences from abstract Truck class. These include the capacity, temperature and the method of finding the cost.
    Author:
    Chris Martin
